<link rel="match" href="reference/white-space-pre-wrap-trailing-spaces-alt-004-ref.html">
<meta name="assert" content="Preserved white space at the end of a soft-wrapped line is hanged when white-space is pre-wrap."><span>
</span><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/fonts/ahem.css">
<style><link type="text/css">
div {
  font: 10px/1 Ahem;
}
.ref {
  position: absolute;
  color: red;
  z-index: -1;
}
.ref span { color: green; }
.test {
  color: green;

  width: 5ch;
  white-space: pre-wrap;
  word-break: break-all;
}
</style>

<p>This test passes if there is a green square and no red.
